sub_title: Independent Higher Education Professional, Owner of J.W. Bekink Taaltrainingen.
summary:
After teaching at secondary schools and Schoevers Opleidingen I started J.W. Bekink Taaltrainingen.
I did trainings for individuals and for groups on different levels In Dutch and German. For example for Language Partners, Vrisekoop Talen, Tekom Vertalers, Edufinance, In-Company Talen, Erasmus Universiteit Rotterdam, Mijn Coach, The Square Mile, Haumann Trainingen, Bon Talen & Partners, IVIO-Personeelsbank, Senata B.V. I also helped with Dutch Café from Delkenboot.

Did volunteering for VBB, De Oriënt, Rotterdam.

Volunteering for 2BDutch.nl.

I have a lot of experience in teaching Dutch and German. I had students of all kinds of nationalities.

I also translate documents and websites D-G, G-D.
